      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl is an exceptional find for a buyer seeking luxury without the showroom price tag. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, showing only the lightest evidence of careful road use, such as a few tiny stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is remarkably clean; the seats are supple, the cabin is smoke-free, and the genuine wood trim remains free of cracks or fading. Every feature\u2014from the power liftgate and panoramic sunroof to the premium Mark Levinson sound system\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, this SUV is in peak form. It has been serviced exclusively at the dealership on a strict schedule, and I have the full binder of maintenance records to prove it. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It offers a whisper-quiet ride and the legendary reliability Lexus is known for. This is a well-loved, honest vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
